  <display_name>HVAC Exhaust Air Energy or Heat Recovery</display_name>
  <description>Adds a heat recovery system to all air loops.  Does not replace or update efficiencies for exisiting heat recovery systems. Excludes food service building types.</description>
  <modeler_description>Heat/energy recovery added based on climate zone. Energy recovery added to ASHRAE 'humid' climates, heat recovery added to all others. Effectivness is based on Ventacity system. Additional fan static pressure is added as wheel power to capture impact of bypass.</modeler_description>
